		  https://besjournals.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/pdf/10.1111/1365-2435.12692},
  keywords	= {phytoliths, evolution, adaptation, herbivore defence,
		  plant silica, structural support},
  file		= {Full Text
		  PDF:/home/isaac/Zotero/storage/7IH58S2P/Strömberg et al. -
